#hes-38-17 {
 {
  → biblisches/Eigene-Uebersetzung/Konkordanz/Knecht#meine-knechte-die-propheten
 }
 {
  TODO: Wo/wann haben welche Propheten was geweissagt?
  <span class='u'>
    Ken Johnson: Ezekiel 38 states other prophets had prophesied about
    the Gog-Magog war in the past, but we do not find any of these
    prophecies in Scripture. The odd placing of "years" after many days
    could be translated "two" instead of "years." In this case the
    passage might be saying "my two prophets of Israel."
    Vgl <a class='kom' href='#I4mo-11-26'>4.&nbsp;Mo&nbsp;11,26</a>.
  </span>
 }
#}
